INSERT INTO `store_items` (`id`, `item_title`, `item_url`, `item_price`, `item_description`, `big_pic`, `small_pic`, `was_price`, `status`) VALUES
(1, 'YAMAHA RYDEEN 20\" ROCK FUSION DRUM KIT WITH HARDWARE IN BURGUNDY GLITTER', 'YAMAHA-RYDEEN-20-ROCK-FUSION-DRUM-KIT-WITH-HARDWARE-IN-BURGUNDY-GLITTER', '450.00', '<h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(24, 24, 24); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">YAMAHA RYDEEN 5 PIECE ROCK FUSION ACOUSTIC DRUM KIT IN BURGUNDY GLITTER WITH 680W HARDWARE</font></h2><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">Inspired by the Japanese God of Thunder, Yamaha Music bring you Rydeen. A durable and dependable 5 piece acoustic drum kit that is brimming with quality, so much so, this kit is rated up their with much more expensive kits but for so much less. A true example of best quality, Yamaha Music have squeezed 50 years\' experience of Professional Drum Making into this one drum kit, pretty impressive right? Well it doesn\'t stop there, Rydeen is full of impressive quirks and qualities that will keep amazing you!</font></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">Crafted using 6-ply Poplar shells, these shells are rounded to perfection. The Poplar shells provide optimum soft high and mid tones as well as a warm, rich low-end. The Rydeen shells&nbsp;deliver smooth, strong sounds across all shell sizes and are all fitted with Yamaha quality metals parts, including top of the range Yamaha Ball Camp and Tom Holders which allow for enhanced stability and freedom when setting up and using your kit.&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">In addition to the beautiful Rydeen Drums, is a genuine Yamaha 680W Hardware set, this</span>&nbsp;very hardware is used on even the most expensive kits from the Yamaha range, be rest assured the quality of hardware is fluid throughout this kit. The Rydeen 20\" Rock Fusion configuration includes 20\" Bass Drum, 10\" and 12\" Toms, 14\" Floor Tom and 14\" Snare Drum so you\'ll have all you need to wow a crowd!</font></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">The Rydeen Series is available in six solid and glitter finishes, each with their own unique appeal. This particular finish is Burgundy Glitter, the finite glitter finish is complimented by the vibrantly stylish deep shade of burgundy. Each shell&nbsp;from the Rydeen Series is wrapped ensuring the longevity of finish and durability of each drum. Yamaha want this to be the drum kit you spend hours and hours practicing on and when it comes to your big debut moment, that the finish looks just as good as the day you bought it.</font></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: basel