(6, 'YAMAHA TOUR CUSTOM 20', 'YAMAHA-TOUR-CUSTOM-20', '1644.00', '<h2 class=\"open\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(24, 24, 24); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">YAMAHA&nbsp;TOUR CUSTOM ACOUSTIC&nbsp;SHELL PACK</font></h2><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">The Yamaha Tour Custom 20\" Fusion 4 Piece Shell Pack is a dynamic series of drum sets which are brand new to Drum Shop. The Tour Custom Series was released by Yamaha Drums in September 2017 and is now&nbsp;turning&nbsp;heads here at our very own, Drum Shop.</font></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">The Tour Custom Maple Traditional Satin Series has been created with the view of combining projection and expression together to create a series of acoustic drum kits that are capable, reliable and above all professional. Yamaha have merged years and years of reputable drum building knowledge and history and designed the Tour Custom Series with close consultation with Yamaha\'s worldwide artist family.</font></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">Following on from the Yamaha Original Absolute Seri