(9, 'YAMAHA 9000 RECORDING CUSTOM 4-PIECE SHELL PACK IN SOLID BLACK', 'YAMAHA-9000-RECORDING-CUSTOM-4-PIECE-SHELL-PACK-IN-SOLID-BLACK', '3020.00', '<h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(24, 24, 24); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">NEW YAMAHA RECORDING CUSTOM DRUM KIT.</font></h2><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><font face=\"Arial\">PRE-ORDER TODAY!</font></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">News just in! We have just been told by our team at NAMM 2016 that Yamaha have launched their brand new Yamaha drum kit and my goodness it\'s just lovely!&nbsp;</font></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">We\'re so excited about the new Yamaha 9000 drums that we\'re ordered them straight from sunny LA, NAMM and they\'ll be on their way to us very soon! Included in our Yamaha order is this 4-Piece Yamaha Recording Custom in&nbsp;Solid Black.</font></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; paddin