(17, 'YAMAHA RYDEEN 20 ROCK FUSION DRUM KIT WITH HARDWARE AND CYMBAL PACK IN MELLOW YELLOW', 'YAMAHA-RYDEEN-20-ROCK-FUSION-DRUM-KIT-WITH-HARDWARE-AND-CYMBAL-PACK-IN-MELLOW-YELLOW', '656.00', '<h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(24, 24, 24); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">YAMAHA RYDEEN 5 PIECE ROCK FUSION ACOUSTIC DRUM KIT IN MELLOW YELLOW&nbsp;WITH HARDWARE AND CYMBAL PACK</font></h2><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">Fancy owning your very own piece of sunshine? Well this is probably the closest you\'re going to get to that! Introducing the Rydeen Series Acoustic Drum Kit in a striking Mellow Yellow finish!&nbsp;</font></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">Yamaha Music have created the creme de la creme of drum kits aimed towards entry level drummers. This 5 piece acoustic drum kit holds onto all the great qualities Yamaha Percussion is renowned for, such as durability, dependability and an overall outstanding performance capacity. Crafted using 6-ply Poplar shells, these shells are rounded to perfection. The Poplar shells provide optimum soft high and mid tones as well as a warm, rich low-end. The Rydeen shells deliver smooth, strong sounds across all shell sizes and are all fitted with Yamaha quality metals parts, including top of the range Yamaha Ball Camp and Tom Holders which allow for enhanced stability and freedom when setting up and using your kit, there\'s no need to worry about your drums they\'re going nowhere! Yamaha have created Rydeen with the sole goal of making drumming easily accessible to beginner or entry level drummers.&nbsp;<br><br>With a Rock Fusion configuration, this drum kit includes 20\" Bass Drum, 10\" and 12\" Toms, 14\" Floor Tom and 14\" Snare Drum; as well as genuine Yamaha 680W Hardware and Yamaha branded Paiste 101 Cymbal Pack. Yamaha 680 Hardware includes Yamaha\'s Professional Series Tom Holders, upgraded Bass Drum legs, Chain Drive Bass Drum Pedal, two Boom Cymbal Stands, Floor Tom brackets and Snare throw off. This very hardware is used on even the most expensive kits from the Yamaha range, be rest assured the quality of hardware is fluid throughout this kit. Also included is the Yamaha branded Paiste 101 Cymbal Pack, tailored towards students or entry level drummers, this cymbal pack is capable of achieving harmonious yet powerful sound. Perfect for live playing, this cymbal pack oozes quality and&nbsp;is very affordable. With all the extra add ons included alongside this kit, you really have everything you need to get started instantaneously.&nbsp;<br><br>The Rydeen Series is available in six solid and glitter finishes, each with their own unique appeal. This particular finish is Mellow Yellow, a striking colour that certainly won\'t fail to be noticed. With a certain 70\'s feel, we can\'t help but feel that this kit is slightly reminiscent of Jazz musician Elvin Jones. Each shell from the Rydeen Series is wrapped ensuring the longevity of finish and durability of each drum. Yamaha want this to be the drum kit you spend hours and hours practicing on and when it comes to your big debut moment, that the finish looks just as good as the day you bought it.<br><br>With over 50 years of drum making experience, Yamaha knew exactly what they were doing when they created this acoustic drum kit known 