(71, 'SAKAE PAC D COMPACT 4-PIECE SHELL PACK', 'SAKAE-PAC-D-COMPACT-4-PIECE-SHELL-PACK', '499.00', '<h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Lato; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(24, 24, 24); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">SAKAE PAC D COMPACT SHELL PACK.</h2><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; font-family: Lato; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Please note this Sakae drum kit&nbsp;does not come with hardware. If you need hardware check out the&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.drumshop.co.uk/products/sakae-pac-d-compact-4-piece-drum-kit?variant=1016136724\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Sakae Pac D drum kit with hardware\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">Pac D with hardware</a>!</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; font-family: Lato; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">This beautiful Sakae Pac D is probably one of the most coolest compact drum kits on the market. If you like them small but fear that you are going to lose the power then this Sakae PD-4 Complete is going to absolutely blow you away! Built from Asian mahogany with a cherry wood cosmetic outer ply delivering beautiful warm and punch sounds. Whether you play Jazz, Rock, Pop whatever your style, this Pac D will fulfill all of your drumming needs. 