(81, 'MAPEX TORNADO COMPACT BEGINNER DRUM KIT', 'MAPEX-TORNADO-COMPACT-BEGINNER-DRUM-KIT', '329.00', '<h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(24, 24, 24); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">MAPEX TORNADO SERIES STARTER COMPACT&nbsp;DRUM KIT.</font></h2><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">The Tornado drum kits feature the newly designed Mapex logo, telescopic bass drum spurs and new lug boxes. You’ll find it hard to believe the Tornado’s are starter drum kits with their new make over! These new drum kits now come in a choice of three drum configurations, Fusion, Rock/Fusion and Compact. Mapex have also added a brand new finish to the Tornado drum kits… Royal Blue! (please ring for this colour)</font></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">If you’re looking for a beginner drum kit for a new drummer then you’re in the right place! Mapex drums are the current brand leaders here at Drum Shop UK and we can see (and hear!) why!&nbsp;</font></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">The Mapex Tornado drum kit has been recognised for the best in performance, value and quality and we think it’s one of the best entry level drum kits out there. This Mapex starter drum kit comes complete with everything you need to enter the world of drumming including 5-piece Mapex hardware pack and two Mapex cymbals.</font></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">For your choice of colour please select from the drop down menu in the Options Panel above.</font></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(24, 24, 24); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">HOW DO I KNOW I’M CHOOSING THE RIGHT DRUM KIT?!</font></h3><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">Many customers get confused about drum sizes and which configuration is going to best for them. There’s a choice of Rock/Fusion, Fusion, or Compact for these starter drum kits…</font></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">The&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.drumshop.co.uk/collections/acoustic-drum-kits/products/mapex-tornado-rock-fusion-beginner-drum-kit?variant=665741849\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Buy Mapex Tornado Series Rock Fusion Drum Kit at Drumshop\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">Rock/Fusion drum configuration</a>&nbsp;is a standard set-up and typically consists of a 22” bass drum, 10” and 12” Toms, 16” Floor tom and a 14” snare drum.</font></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">The&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.drumshop.co.uk/collections/acoustic-drum-kits/products/mapex-tornado-fusion-beginner-drum-kit?variant=665728997\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Buy Mapex Tornado Drum Kit from Drumshop UK\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">Fusion drum configuration</a>&nbsp;is ideal for the younger drummer as the set-up tends to be smaller, with a 20” bass drum, 10” and 12” Toms, 14” Floor tom and a 14” snare drum.</font></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">The Compact drum configuration is smaller still with a 18” bass drum, 10” and 12” toms, 14” floor tom and 14” snare drum. This is also known as the Junior drum kit as it’s aimed towards children, but is also the ideal set-up for smaller bedrooms, hence the name \'compact’. This configuration comes with a smaller heigh snare stand and throne also. All three set-ups include 5 drums.</font></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"http://www.drumshop.co.uk/pages/new-to-drumming\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Information for new drummers. Drumshop UK\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\"><font face=\"Arial\">If you\'re a beginner&nbsp;drummer and you\'re looking for some more information, check out our \'new to drumming\' page by&nbsp;clicking&nbsp;here!</font></span></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(24, 24, 24); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">FEATURES:</font></h3><ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none outside; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.2; vertical-align: baseline;\