(100, 'YAMAHA DTX 522K ELECTRONIC DRUM KIT', 'YAMAHA-DTX-522K-ELECTRONIC-DRUM-KIT', '852.00', '<h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Lato; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(24, 24, 24); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">NEW YAMAHA DTX522K DRUM KIT.</h2><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; font-family: Lato; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The Yamaha&nbsp;<span class=\"caps\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">DTX</span>&nbsp;digital drum are a popular choice for drummers of all levels and now there are even more of these electronic drum kits to choose from!<br>The DTX522K electronic drum kit is a new addition to the Yamaha&nbsp;<span class=\"caps\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">DTX</span>&nbsp;family and comes complete with new and improved features including the DTX502 module which is packed with over 650 drum sounds! The DTX522K drum kit allows you to practice without annoying the neighbours and still have that all important natural playing feel thanks to the cleverly designed drum pads. The 522K drum kit is built on the Yamaha RS502 drum rack which is both strong and durable and also easy to assemble and tear-down! If you’re a left handed player, you can simply re-arrange your set-up on the drum rack withou