(118, 'YAMAHA RECORDING CUSTOM 14\" X 5.5\" BRASS SNARE DRUM', 'YAMAHA-RECORDING-CUSTOM-14-X-55-BRASS-SNARE-DRUM', '426.00', '<h2 style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 28px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(24, 24, 24); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">YAMAHA RECORDING CUSTOM SNARE DRUM.</font></h2><p style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">The Yamaha Recording Custom Brass snare drums are available in three sizes; 13\" x 6.5\", 14\" x 5.5\" and 14\" x 6.5\", all of which are available at buy online at drumshop!</font></p><p style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">These Yamaha snare drums are a new addition to the popular Metal Series and are packed with top-end features resulting in some of the finest metal drums around! This Recording Custom snare drum features a 1.2mm Brass drum shell with an outward centre bead which provides you with a more open and crisp sound than previous models. This feature came about after many evaluations from Steve Gadd, as traditionally, the metal centre bead was on the interior of the drum.</font></p><p style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; b