(119, 'YAMAHA ABSOLUTE HYBRID MAPLE 14 X 6 ORANGE SPARKLE SNARE DRUM', 'YAMAHA-ABSOLUTE-HYBRID-MAPLE-14-X-6-ORANGE-SPARKLE-SNARE-DRUM', '511.00', '<h2 class=\"trigger open\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; border: none; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; cursor: pointer; background: url(&quot;icon-arrow-down-grey.png&quot;) right center no-repeat rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">DESCRIPTION</font></h2><div class=\"content-panel rte clearfix open\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; zoom: 1; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(24, 24, 24); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;\"><font face=\"Arial\">YAMAHA MAPLE HYBRID 14\" X 6\" SNARE DRUM IN ORANGE SPARKLE</font></h2><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\"><font face=\"Arial\">When Yamaha decided to design the hybrid maple snare drum, they thought about the most important thing of all... the sound. From a slight rattle to a loud crash this snare should give you everything