(120, 'SONOR SQ1 SERIES 14 X 6.5 SNARE DRUM IN CRUISER BLUE', 'SONOR-SQ1-SERIES-14-X-65-SNARE-DRUM-IN-CRUISER-BLUE', '220.00', '<h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(24, 24, 24); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">SONOR&nbsp;SQ1&nbsp;CRUISER BLUE SNARE DRUM</font></h2><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">Sonor SQ1 as a series has been heavily inspired by timeless cars, whose performance, visual aesthetic and quality is classically sought after and always remembered. Sonor takes these qualities and successfully translates them into workable, useable percussion products and the SQ1 series is proof of that.&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">This particular SQ1 snare drum has been constructed using 100% European birch shell and the result is just irresistible. Birch itself&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">has a flexible and versatile range of capabilities, it creates a blend of sound that is ideal for any setting or atmosphere, but&nbsp;the&nbsp;versatility works extremely well in studio settings, the sound produced translates impeccably well when recorded.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;Not only does this SQ1 snare sound amazing, the aesthetic isn\'t too shabby either! The high quality cruiser blue lacquer finish is just dreamy, perfectly matte and undeniably cool, it is complimented with 45 degree bearing edges and the super suave Sonor SQ1 drum badge.</span></font></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">Sonor SQ1 snare drums have a bundle of features which all contribute to making&nbsp;them&nbsp;snares proud to hold the Sonor badge. From Optimum Shell Measurement (OLM) Shell Sizing to Dual Glide Snare System (Snare Quick Release), Cross Lamination Tension Free Construction (CLTF) to Tune Safe Lugs and not forgetting the fantastic Remo Ambassador Coated Heads. Sonor\'s (CLTF) Cross Lamination Tension Free and (OSM) Optimum Shell Measurement are&nbsp;key features in the SQ1 Series, both save you time and maximise your playing time with your SQ1 snare drum. Not only that CLTF ensures your snare drum is protected even under immense playing pressure and demands. Standard in all Sonor snare drums, Tune Safe lugs contribute to keeping you in tune time and time again, not some of the time,&nbsp;ALL of the time! A true workhorse, this Sonor SQ1 snare is inspired by classic cars, created by masters of percussion manufacturing and owned by you, the drummer of the future!</font></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(24, 24, 24); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">FEATUR