(122, 'SONOR VINTAGE SERIES 14 X 6.5 SNARE DRUM IN VINTAGE RED OYSTER', 'SONOR-VINTAGE-SERIES-14-X-65-SNARE-DRUM-IN-VINTAGE-RED-OYSTER', '660.00', '<h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(24, 24, 24); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">SONOR&nbsp;VINTAGE&nbsp;SERIES VINTAGE&nbsp;RED OYSTER SNARE DRUM</font></h2><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">Ever sat and yearned to create the iconic sounds of the past yourself and not just be content with listening to them on old school recording? Well move over drummers the Sonor Vintage Series is here and you no longer have to dream about creating those sounds, it\'s now very much a reality! The Vintage Series from Sonor celebrates the sound, the look and the feel of those vintage kits that made Sonor so iconic back in the 1950\'s. Hand selected German beech wood is the shell base for this snare drum and the snare has rounded, vintage style bearing edges which make for a warm resonance due to the increased head to shell contact when in use.</font></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">The redesigned Super 50 strainer is a reinvention of strainers used in the classic snare drums from the 1950\'s, the Sonor D-411 and Sonor D-412. Tune Safe technology is as standard with all Sonor snare drums and it allows you to be tuned in 100% of the time,