(144, 'SAKAE TRILOGY 14 X 6.5 SNARE DRUM IN BLACK OYSTER PEARL', 'SAKAE-TRILOGY-14-X-65-SNARE-DRUM-IN-BLACK-OYSTER-PEARL', '499.00', '<h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(24, 24, 24); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">BLACK OYSTER PEARL SNARE DRUM.</font></h2><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">Each and every Sakae drum has been build in Osaka, Japan by high quality Japanese drum manufacturer, Sakae Rhythm. With over 40 years of drum building experience, Sakae have moulded into a trusted brand and are growing everyday. There are many professional drummers playing Sakae drums including Ash Soan, Neal Wilkinson, Steve Jordan, Jack Pollitt and many more.</font></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">The Sakae Trilogy series has been built to give you the all important distinctive Sakae sound combined with the timeless vintage qualities which are still loved after all these years. This 14” x 6.5” Sakae snare drum comes in an eye catching black oyster pearl finish and sounds amazing no matter what you’re playing! This Trilogy snare drum is constructed from a 3-ply Maple/Poplar/Maple shell complete with 4-ply North American Maple reinforcement rings.</font></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\"><br></font></p><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/-p89MWDvrAk\" frameborder=\"0\" gesture=\"media\" allow=\"encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>', 'Sakae-Trilogy-14_-x-5_5_-Snare-Drum-In-Black-Oyster-Pearl_1c7783c2-d94e-4e0f-8f3e-280cfd8033b2.jpg', 'Sakae-Trilogy-14_-x-5_5_-Snare-Drum-In-Black-Oyster-Pearl_1c7783c2-d94e-4e0f-8f3e-280cfd8033b2.jpg', '0.00', 1),
