(156, 'DREAM BLISS SERIES PAPER THIN CRASH CYMBAL 19\"', 'DREAM-BLISS-SERIES-PAPER-THIN-CRASH-CYMBAL-19', '156.00', '<h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(24, 24, 24); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">DREAM BLISS PAPER THIN 19\" CRASH CYMBAL</font></h2><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">The Bliss Paper Thin Series from Dream pride themselves on the hand rendered techniques used in every cymbal. Individuality and craftsmanship are embedded into each Dream cymbal using hand hammering and the Paper Thin Series is no different. Although ultra thin, don\'t let this deceive you, the Paper Thin Series are full of shimmer and excel within many&nbsp;volume settings. Exceptional resilience synonymous with the Dream brand is at the forefront of this series. The Paper Thin Series comes alive at the slightest touch, a cymbal that can\'t wait to be heard.&nbsp;</font></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">The Bliss 19\" Paper Thin Crash Cymbal is exceptionally resilient,&nbsp;full of character and creates a unique crash sound. The cymbal comes alive with the slightest touch and this enhances its charm even more. Dark rich undertones are woven into each&nbsp;cymbal making them ideal for a range of&nbsp;musical settings that require intimate, low volume output. The hand crafted nature of the Paper Thin Series, enables the cymbal to be particularly durable whilst&nbsp;retaining an unforgettable softness.</font></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(24, 24, 24); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">FEATURES:</font></h3><ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none outside; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\"><font face=\"Arial\">Surface: Micro-lathed by hand</font></li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\"><font face=\"Arial\">Bow: Low gentle bridge</font></li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\"><font face=\"Arial\">Bell: Small, articulate, clear</font></li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\"><font face=\"Arial\">Weight: Thin tapers towards edge</font></li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\"><font face=\"Arial\">Hammering: Hand hammered (both before and after lathing)</font></li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\"><font face=\"Arial\">Stick: Woody round attack</font></li></ul><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(24, 24, 24); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">SIZE:</font></h3><ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none outside; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><font face=\"Arial\">19\" Paper Thin Crash Cymbal</font></span></li></ul><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(24, 24