(179, 'STAGG 10\" + 16\" SENSA SIZZLE STACK', 'STAGG-10-16-SENSA-SIZZLE-STACK', '138.00', '<h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(24, 24, 24); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">STAGG 10\" + 16\" SENSA SIZZLE STACK</font></h2><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">This fast and punchy&nbsp;SENSA Sizzle Stack from Stagg features added subtle sustain due to the rivets. This sizzle stack is ideally suited for quick rhythms or it can be used as a ride source. The pack contains a 10\" splash and a 16\" sizzle china cymbal.</font></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: none; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(24, 24, 24); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font face=\"Arial\">SIZE:</font></h3><ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none outside; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inhe